  "text": "The aim of this study was to validate HADS and BDI self-report rating scales as screening measures for the detection of depression in ESRD patients. HADS, which has not previously been validated in this patient group, was compared with BDI, which was validated three times in ESRD patients. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] Both scales were compared to the diagnosis major depressive episode based on the MINI.",
